text: Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny is a 2023 American action adventure movie directed by James Mangold. It stars Harrison Ford, Phoebe Waller-Bridge, Antonio Banderas, John Rhys-Davies, Toby Jones, Boyd Holbrook, Ethann Isidore, Mads Mikkelsen and Karen Allen. The movie was released on May 25, 2023. It was a box office bomb.
